Package AdventureModel

Class Passage

java.lang.Object
AdventureModel.Passage
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Passage extends Object implements Serializable
The Passage class represents entries in a passage table. A passage keeps track of information about an exit from a room. This includes the direction of the exit and the room number. If the passage is blocked, the passage keeps track of the key required to move along this passage.
